These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, raspberry
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, punk
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, chaman
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the chaman-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the person playing poker is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | raspberry  | pineapple     |
| Flower         | dahlia    | rose         |
| Game           | scrabble    | poker |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | punk     |
| Pet           | horse      | chinchilla    |
| Cigar         | chaman | bolivar          |

