.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, social-worker
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, poppy
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, russian
2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice
1. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Sport         | sailing      | climbing       |
| Job           | entrepreneur | social-worker |
| Food   | watermelon      | cauliflower        |
| Flower   | aconite         | poppy        |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | russian       |
| Pet           | mouse        | goat          |
| Beverage     | juice          | iced-tea    |

