.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, crime
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian
2 different games are played: backgammon, chess
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
2. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the argentine##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | soy-milk  |
| Movie-Genre          | crime   | horror   |
| Cigar         | blend | old-henry   |
| Music-Genre           | r&b        | gospel   |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | argentine |
| Game         | chess    | backgammon  |
| Transport     | scooter       | taxi      |

